1
00:00:41,120 --> 00:00:41,960
This woman

2
00:00:42,240 --> 00:00:43,440
sleeps so poorly.

3
00:00:43,840 --> 00:00:45,370
She has no vigilance at all.

4
00:00:45,960 --> 00:00:47,440
I wonder which idiot

5
00:00:47,760 --> 00:00:50,220
sent such a piece of trash to assassinate me.

6
00:00:56,120 --> 00:00:56,880
Perfect.

7
00:00:57,480 --> 00:00:59,410
Let's see if these inferior things

8
00:00:59,520 --> 00:01:01,080
can test her background.

9
00:01:09,280 --> 00:01:10,080
Help!

10
00:01:12,160 --> 00:01:13,600
Why are you in my room?

11
00:01:19,920 --> 00:01:20,640
Consciousness,

12
00:01:20,640 --> 00:01:21,720
World Consciousness,

13
00:01:21,720 --> 00:01:22,960
come out quickly!

14
00:01:23,280 --> 00:01:24,280
Help!

15
00:01:24,760 --> 00:01:26,200
Didn't you say I could use magic?

16
00:01:26,200 --> 00:01:27,200
Where is my magic?

17
00:01:47,520 --> 00:01:48,600
Source blood.

18
00:01:51,280 --> 00:01:53,410
Someone from the Heavenly Dao Palace.

19
00:01:58,400 --> 00:01:59,360
Your Majesty,

20
00:01:59,840 --> 00:02:01,480
my flesh doesn't taste good.

21
00:02:03,120 --> 00:02:03,600
No.

22
00:02:03,880 --> 00:02:05,480
With such pure source blood,

23
00:02:05,680 --> 00:02:07,920
how could the Heavenly Dao Palace let her wander outside?

24
00:02:07,920 --> 00:02:10,680
The world consciousness only told me about the Great Demon King's cruelty,

25
00:02:10,680 --> 00:02:12,360
but it didn't say he eats people.

26
00:02:12,360 --> 00:02:14,720
How did I enter such a terrifying world?

27
00:02:15,400 --> 00:02:16,880
Just this little bit of blood

28
00:02:16,880 --> 00:02:18,810
has made my body recover somewhat.

29
00:02:19,000 --> 00:02:19,730
As expected,

30
00:02:20,000 --> 00:02:21,400
the purest source blood

31
00:02:21,680 --> 00:02:24,140
is the most suitable cultivation material.

32
00:02:24,440 --> 00:02:26,240
What a perfect sacrifice.

33
00:02:27,040 --> 00:02:28,440
What should I do with you?

34
00:02:36,480 --> 00:02:38,280
Did I just dodge a disaster?

35
00:03:03,720 --> 00:03:04,560
My Lord.

36
00:03:05,240 --> 00:03:06,720
What exactly do you want?

37
00:03:07,000 --> 00:03:07,800
I can't sleep.

38
00:03:10,480 --> 00:03:11,280
I...

39
00:03:13,400 --> 00:03:14,860
Let me put some clothes on.

40
00:03:17,920 --> 00:03:19,880
Your condition is still unstable, sir.

41
00:03:19,880 --> 00:03:21,720
You really should get more rest.

42
00:03:22,200 --> 00:03:24,240
Even if you can't sleep in the middle of the night,

43
00:03:24,240 --> 00:03:25,720
you should just lie down.

44
00:03:26,200 --> 00:03:27,280
Sir.

45
00:03:27,880 --> 00:03:30,120
Why aren't you calling me 'My Lord' anymore?

46
00:03:30,120 --> 00:03:31,160
A slip of the tongue.

47
00:03:31,160 --> 00:03:32,200
How could a noble

48
00:03:32,280 --> 00:03:34,040
and righteous hero like you

49
00:03:34,360 --> 00:03:35,400
be associated with

50
00:03:35,400 --> 00:03:36,200
a title like

51
00:03:36,200 --> 00:03:37,240
'My Lord'?

52
00:03:38,320 --> 00:03:40,120
Speaking of the title 'My Lord',

53
00:03:40,440 --> 00:03:43,120
I think the Demon Lord who is about to break the seal

54
00:03:43,120 --> 00:03:44,579
is much more suited for it.

55
00:03:44,960 --> 00:03:45,640
Don't you

56
00:03:45,960 --> 00:03:46,640
think so?

57
00:03:48,560 --> 00:03:49,960
Demon Lord or not,

58
00:03:50,079 --> 00:03:51,600
how could a nobody like me

59
00:03:51,840 --> 00:03:52,640
possibly know

60
00:03:52,840 --> 00:03:54,370
information of that level?

61
00:03:55,760 --> 00:03:56,890
Not only do you know,

62
00:03:57,320 --> 00:03:59,400
but you've also been in contact with him.

63
00:03:59,400 --> 00:04:00,480
How is that possible?

64
00:04:00,480 --> 00:04:02,000
Is he laying his cards on the table?

65
00:04:02,000 --> 00:04:03,440
Is he going to silence me?

66
00:04:05,600 --> 00:04:08,560
Didn't you just get poisoned by the Nether Poison a couple of days ago, Miss Lu?

67
00:04:08,560 --> 00:04:09,880
Those Nether Demons

68
00:04:10,080 --> 00:04:12,160
used to all be his subordinates.

69
00:04:15,160 --> 00:04:16,519
I see.

70
00:04:16,720 --> 00:04:17,760
I haven't read much,

71
00:04:17,760 --> 00:04:19,920
so I don't know if you're lying to me.

72
00:04:21,160 --> 00:04:23,420
I heard this Demon Lord is cruel by nature

73
00:04:23,520 --> 00:04:24,880
and hates humans.

74
00:04:25,640 --> 00:04:27,240
Once he comes into the world,

75
00:04:27,480 --> 00:04:30,210
I'm afraid the world will be plunged into misery.

76
00:04:30,760 --> 00:04:31,360
Tell me,

77
00:04:32,000 --> 00:04:34,130
shouldn't we think of a way to stop him?

78
00:04:34,400 --> 00:04:35,840
You've already escaped.

79
00:04:36,000 --> 00:04:38,060
What's the use of talking about this?

80
00:04:39,320 --> 00:04:41,120
This Demon Lord is so great,

81
00:04:41,159 --> 00:04:42,640
how can nobodies like us

82
00:04:42,760 --> 00:04:44,040
casually discuss him?

83
00:04:44,240 --> 00:04:45,840
I should probably head back.

84
00:04:47,920 --> 00:04:49,040
If it were you,

85
00:04:49,480 --> 00:04:50,480
what would you do?

86
00:04:51,720 --> 00:04:54,450
While he is powerless to break free from the seal,

87
00:04:54,600 --> 00:04:56,800
kill him before he wakes up.

88
00:04:58,280 --> 00:05:00,340
How could I have that kind of ability?

89
00:05:00,360 --> 00:05:01,490
Since I'm so useless

90
00:05:01,520 --> 00:05:03,160
that I couldn't even dodge the Nether Poison,

91
00:05:03,160 --> 00:05:04,690
dealing with the Demon Lord

92
00:05:04,840 --> 00:05:06,640
shouldn't be my concern, right?

93
00:05:10,920 --> 00:05:11,840
That's true.

94
00:05:12,240 --> 00:05:13,840
You are indeed very useless.

95
00:05:14,600 --> 00:05:15,480
Fine.

96
00:05:15,760 --> 00:05:17,720
Humiliation is better than being killed.

97
00:05:17,720 --> 00:05:18,000
Yes.

98
00:05:18,800 --> 00:05:20,000
Operations like this

99
00:05:20,160 --> 00:05:22,560
should be left to a great hero like you.

100
00:05:22,800 --> 00:05:23,730
Good luck to you.

101
00:05:27,080 --> 00:05:29,140
Tonight's chat was really pleasant.

102
00:05:29,840 --> 00:05:30,520
Then I

103
00:05:30,960 --> 00:05:33,290
will not disturb your rest anymore, Miss.

104
00:05:39,440 --> 00:05:41,240
They finally left.

105
00:05:53,200 --> 00:05:54,159
Lanqi Moyuan.

106
00:05:54,400 --> 00:05:55,460
He really escaped.

107
00:05:56,360 --> 00:05:56,840
Chunyi.

108
00:05:57,760 --> 00:05:58,960
Are you talking about

109
00:05:58,960 --> 00:06:00,720
that legendary Demon Lord?

110
00:06:01,560 --> 00:06:02,620
Stop the nonsense.

111
00:06:03,480 --> 00:06:05,410
Lanqi Moyuan has escaped the seal.

112
00:06:05,480 --> 00:06:07,410
The human world will have no peace.

113
00:06:07,640 --> 00:06:08,120
Hurry,

114
00:06:08,480 --> 00:06:09,440
send a message to the palace.

115
00:06:09,440 --> 00:06:09,840
Yes.

116
00:06:24,920 --> 00:06:25,920
Oh, no!

117
00:06:26,200 --> 00:06:26,840
Xiaoxue.

118
00:06:27,280 --> 00:06:28,440
I heard that Tiandao Palace

119
00:06:28,440 --> 00:06:29,320
discovered that the Lord of the Netherworld

120
00:06:29,320 --> 00:06:30,000
escaped the seal.

121
00:06:30,000 --> 00:06:30,840
Just yesterday.

122
00:06:30,840 --> 00:06:31,440
What?

123
00:06:31,880 --> 00:06:32,680
Are you talking

124
00:06:32,680 --> 00:06:34,120
about the legendary Demon Lord?

125
00:06:34,120 --> 00:06:34,480
Yes.

126
00:06:34,680 --> 00:06:36,880
The very one who strikes fear into the Tiandao Palace,

127
00:06:36,880 --> 00:06:37,920
the Lord of the Netherworld.

128
00:06:37,920 --> 00:06:38,760
This is bad.

129
00:06:39,320 --> 00:06:41,560
A large number of Nether Demons have already appeared in the mortal world.

130
00:06:41,560 --> 00:06:42,159
And now...

131
00:06:42,280 --> 00:06:43,560
I'm afraid it's even harder to stop.

132
00:06:43,560 --> 00:06:44,880
With such a big thing happening,

133
00:06:44,880 --> 00:06:46,560
Tiandao Palace won't just sit back and do nothing.

134
00:06:46,560 --> 00:06:48,680
We just need to wait for further arrangements.

135
00:06:48,680 --> 00:06:49,560
That's true.

136
00:06:50,040 --> 00:06:51,920
Tiandao Palace, as the leader of the human race,

137
00:06:51,920 --> 00:06:52,960
since its establishment,

138
00:06:52,960 --> 00:06:54,920
has always been working hard for the livelihood of the human race.

139
00:06:54,920 --> 00:06:56,920
A huge matter like the escape of the Demon Lord this time,

140
00:06:56,920 --> 00:06:58,920
they will definitely take it very seriously.

141
00:06:58,920 --> 00:06:59,720
It's just that...

142
00:06:59,720 --> 00:07:01,160
I wonder how many disciples will be needed

143
00:07:01,160 --> 00:07:02,160
to deal with this.

144
00:07:02,440 --> 00:07:03,200
I think,

145
00:07:03,400 --> 00:07:04,730
at least more than half.

146
00:07:05,680 --> 00:07:06,920
Maybe even more.

147
00:07:07,520 --> 00:07:10,120
Can we not talk about this early in the morning?

148
00:07:10,400 --> 00:07:12,080
What if the Demon Lord hears it?

149
00:07:12,080 --> 00:07:13,280
He's right here.

150
00:07:15,120 --> 00:07:15,800
That's right.

151
00:07:15,800 --> 00:07:16,330
Xiaoxue,

152
00:07:16,600 --> 00:07:17,520
you're right.

153
00:07:20,520 --> 00:07:21,180
Brother Li,

154
00:07:21,240 --> 00:07:21,760
Danyu,

155
00:07:22,080 --> 00:07:23,040
you're all up.

156
00:07:23,720 --> 00:07:24,320
Come,

157
00:07:24,480 --> 00:07:25,740
let's have breakfast.

158
00:07:31,080 --> 00:07:31,680
Li,

159
00:07:32,080 --> 00:07:33,340
how are your injuries?

160
00:07:34,240 --> 00:07:35,900
Thanks to Miss Mu's medicine,

161
00:07:35,920 --> 00:07:37,200
I have fully recovered.

162
00:07:37,200 --> 00:07:38,440
Fighting demons again

163
00:07:38,440 --> 00:07:39,500
won't be a problem.

164
00:07:40,600 --> 00:07:41,640
That's great.

165
00:07:41,760 --> 00:07:42,290
However,

166
00:07:42,480 --> 00:07:43,940
you still need to rest more

167
00:07:44,040 --> 00:07:46,170
so the medicine can fully take effect.

168
00:07:46,560 --> 00:07:47,820
You are right, Miss Mu.

169
00:07:52,040 --> 00:07:52,680
Brother Li,

170
00:07:52,680 --> 00:07:54,280
don't just stand there chatting.

171
00:07:54,280 --> 00:07:55,200
Let's all sit down.

172
00:07:55,200 --> 00:07:55,760
Sit down.

173
00:07:58,120 --> 00:07:59,720
The female lead is getting close to the second male lead,

174
00:07:59,720 --> 00:08:00,480
the male lead is jealous,

175
00:08:00,480 --> 00:08:01,940
and he's trying to ruin it.

176
00:08:02,880 --> 00:08:04,640
This TV drama-like déjà vu,

177
00:08:04,880 --> 00:08:06,340
and it's a live broadcast.

178
00:08:06,480 --> 00:08:08,080
It feels incredibly good.

179
00:08:09,640 --> 00:08:10,770
I am perfectly safe.

180
00:08:13,200 --> 00:08:14,460
However, this Miss Lu,

181
00:08:14,720 --> 00:08:16,200
not only suffered a fright,

182
00:08:16,200 --> 00:08:17,460
but also bled a little.

183
00:08:18,760 --> 00:08:19,320
Danyu,

184
00:08:19,880 --> 00:08:20,880
you're bleeding?

185
00:08:23,640 --> 00:08:24,760
Where are you bleeding?

186
00:08:24,760 --> 00:08:25,960
Is the wound serious?

187
00:08:26,120 --> 00:08:27,640
Last night, while Miss Lu was sleeping,

188
00:08:27,640 --> 00:08:29,570
she was attacked by Nether Demons.

189
00:08:29,840 --> 00:08:30,400
I was duty-bound

190
00:08:30,400 --> 00:08:31,280
to do my best

191
00:08:31,600 --> 00:08:32,400
and managed to

192
00:08:32,440 --> 00:08:33,240
repel them.

193
00:08:33,919 --> 00:08:34,720
What?

194
00:08:35,600 --> 00:08:37,330
Nether Demons attacked Danyu?

195
00:08:37,600 --> 00:08:38,080
Danyu,

196
00:08:38,240 --> 00:08:38,900
how are you?

197
00:08:38,960 --> 00:08:39,440
Are you okay?

198
00:08:39,440 --> 00:08:40,559
I'm fine.

199
00:08:41,320 --> 00:08:42,400
You two were

200
00:08:42,919 --> 00:08:44,120
together last night.

201
00:08:46,080 --> 00:08:46,680
What?

202
00:08:46,880 --> 00:08:47,280
You...

203
00:08:48,160 --> 00:08:50,760
You two were together in the middle of the night?

204
00:08:50,760 --> 00:08:51,400
No.

205
00:08:51,880 --> 00:08:53,560
What do you mean we were together in the middle of the night?

206
00:08:53,560 --> 00:08:54,820
I was clearly sleeping

207
00:08:54,920 --> 00:08:57,080
when suddenly a Ming Demon broke into my room and attacked me.

208
00:08:57,080 --> 00:08:57,410
Then,

209
00:08:57,560 --> 00:08:58,560
he was in my room

210
00:08:58,680 --> 00:08:59,480
helping me fight the Ming Demon.
